      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-alf                to   rr-opz-stp             .
       acc-opz-stp-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-opz-stp-600.
