           move      w-inp-rig            to   srt-rec-inp            .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Record [oft]                        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      rf-oft               to   srt-rec-oft            .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Record [ofr]                        *
