           move      rf-oft-dat-doc       to   w-det-num-oft-dat      .
           move      rf-oft-num-doc       to   w-det-num-oft-num      .
           move      rf-oft-num-prt       to   w-det-num-oft-prt      .
           move      rf-oft-tmo-orf       to   w-det-num-oft-tof      .
