                                          into o-shs                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Richiamo del modulo 'mopsys'                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SH"                 to   o-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase video                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ER"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ripristino immagine video                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Attesa tecnica di 1 secondo                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mwait0"                         .
       del-fls-agb-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
            go to    del-fls-agb-999.
       del-fls-agb-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
