      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "IR"                 to   d-imp-acq-tip-ope      .
           move      rf-ofr-qta-fda       to   d-imp-acq-qta-acq      .
           move      rf-ofr-prz-acq       to   d-imp-acq-prz-uni      .
