           move      rf-ofr-per-scr (1)   to   d-imp-acq-per-scr (1)  .
           move      rf-ofr-per-scr (2)   to   d-imp-acq-per-scr (2)  .
           move      rf-ofr-per-scr (3)   to   d-imp-acq-per-scr (3)  .
           move      rf-ofr-per-scr (4)   to   d-imp-acq-per-scr (4)  .
           move      rf-ofr-per-scr (5)   to   d-imp-acq-per-scr (5)  .
           move      spaces               to   d-imp-acq-tip-clc      .
